This project vendors a patched copy of the hypha-rpc JS bundle
(extension/lib/hypha-rpc.mjs). hypha-rpc is licensed MIT:
https://github.com/oeway/hypha-rpc

The smart-DOM patterns in get_browser_state / click_by_index / input_by_index
are derived from browser-use (https://github.com/browser-use/browser-use) via
hypha-debugger (https://github.com/amun-ai/hypha-debugger). Both MIT-licensed.
Original copyright notices preserved.
